(3) In the Cemiess [-2,-2] system the black marked is totally screwed up.
Listen to this: (from Emerald, Camp Lowing)
At Judd's Trading Company, you can get Precious Metals for -3189.0 c 
(notice the '-' sign) and Gem Stones for -564.8 c (again, notice the 
'-' sign). Jesssir, that's right, we will pay YOU 3189 cool credits 
for each ton of filthy gold you can free us from. Dump it, sell it in
a nearby system, we don't care. Just remember when you get back, there
will be more waiting for you!!! 
Christ, I played for about 3 hours and upped my cash from 30000 c to
600000 c switching ship TWICE. Then I got sick of it and headed as far
away as I could get in my Imperial Trader (w/ all the cool stuff you
could ever ask for). 

